05:50.851 --> 05:53.253
â™ª Firm and strong â™ª

05:53.253 --> 05:55.856
â™ª All the ones who make you catch â™ª

05:55.856 --> 05:57.724
â™ª Are cursed dogs â™ª

06:02.329 --> 06:03.797
- (sobbing)
- â™ª Suffocate â™ª

06:08.602 --> 06:11.038
â™ª Stay awake, save a plate â™ª

06:11.038 --> 06:13.640
â™ª Count your treats â™ª

06:13.640 --> 06:16.043
â™ª Make you melt, make you feel â™ª

