â™ª Suffocate â™ª

06:38.298 --> 06:40.601
(rock music continues)

06:44.571 --> 06:46.573
This is ridiculous.

06:46.573 --> 06:47.674
I'm not an addict.

06:47.674 --> 06:51.044
If I was, wouldn't I have
been Lohan-ing in detox?

06:51.044 --> 06:52.913
Getting my drivers license was more taxing.

06:52.913 --> 06:55.282
Why? Why are you doing this to me?

06:55.282 --> 06:56.884
This is so unfair!

06:56.884 --> 06:58.852
This is your fault. I hate you!

06:58.852 --> 07:00.587
Tell you what...

07:00.587 --> 07:02.322
why don't I just stay home every night?

07:02.322 --> 07:04.758
You can monitor me, smell my breath,

07:04.758 --> 07:06.693
make me pee in a cup.

07:06.693 --> 07:08.829
I hate everything.

07:12.733 --> 07:13.834
(sighs)

07:30.617 --> 07:33.720
(people chatting, applause)

07:37.658 --> 07:39.726
(people greeting)

07:47.668 --> 07:49.603
(upbeat music playing)

07:49.603 --> 07:54.041
